+ Security Considerations\n& Best Practices
++ Never hardcode secrets
+++_ Use Azure Key Vault or Databricks secrets
+++_ Prevents accidental exposure
+++_ Safe for version control
++ Secret rotation
+++_ Client secrets expire
+++_ Must be rotated periodically
+++_ Know the rotation schedule
++ Least privilege
+++_ Specific storage locations only
+++_ Limit blast radius of compromise
